  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK156">
<l>oṟuttārk korunāḷai yiṉpam poṟuttārkkup</l>
<l>poṉṟun tuṇaiyum pukaḻ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The pleasure of the resentful continues for a day. The praise of the patient will continue until (the final destruction of) the world.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
